<h5 class="info">Hi! This game is about the environment. <br>
The goal of this game is to catch as many hazardous things as possible, to save the environment!<br>
Different things have different degradation time, so they have different values as well.<br> 
If you want to study on these things, you can find explanation after the game, in the high score section.<br>
One round takes 60 seconds to complet, this time you have to collect as many garbage as you can!</h5>
